1
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:56,680
Master

2
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,520
Second Uncle's body has been dealt with

3
00:00:58,760 --> 00:00:59,960
There won't be a next time

4
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,480
Next time

5
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:07,160
The Police Station is in chaos, no time for this

6
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,760
But next time we won't be so lucky

7
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:12,360
If the police really press the matter

8
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,800
None of us will get away with it

9
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:22,360
Tea brewed with boiling water has real flavor

10
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,400
Yes, Master

11
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:33,600
How is the Private detective's investigation going?

12
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:36,760
Th-they all say Miss Shuang'er came for lives

13
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,600
No one dares investigate

14
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,960
Even if no one dares, it must be investigated

15
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:46,160
Today they killed my distant relative

16
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,320
Tomorrow it'll be my turn

17
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:52,240
Don't worry, I'll put more pressure on them

18
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,400
What should be checked and what shouldn't

19
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,160
Do they know that clearly?

20
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,440
I know my limits

21
00:01:59,040 --> 00:01:59,720
You know your limits

22
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,760
Madam

23
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:12,880
This is a tonic soup I prepared for you myself

24
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,040
Have a taste

25
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:25,040
As long as you drink it

26
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:27,560
You'll be one of the Wang family

27
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,240
Come on

28
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,320
Master didn't touch me

29
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,720
This wound is

30
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:02,040
Fifth Concubine, you're awake

31
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,480
I've set your breakfast here

32
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,000
Are you feeling unwell?

33
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,240
I'm fine

34
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:20,760
I'm Xiao Ru. Master sent me to serve you

35
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:24,360
I understand. You may go now

36
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,720
Today is my wedding day

37
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,520
I don't want any bad luck on me

38
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,560
I am now the Wang family's Fifth Concubine

39
00:04:21,080 --> 00:04:22,320
I won't go with you

40
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,400
Master

41
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:29,240
Zheng Yu, you're here

42
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,640
I found out

43
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,760
The person who died last night

44
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,640
was the Wang family's Second Uncle

45
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:39,880
Even Wang Shengchang's money got no one to inspect it

46
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,240
If you ask me

47
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,680
Wang Shengchang is truly scared this time

48
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,400
Why are you ignoring me?

49
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:53,520
I've got news about your sister-in-law. Want to hear?

50
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,240
I don't want to hear it

51
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,960
I paid dearly to get this news

52
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:03,960
They say Wang Shengchang can't do it anymore

53
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:06,000
You don't need to worry about being cuckolded

54
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,160
I already have someone I love

55
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,840
No matter what, I won't marry

56
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:27,280
Don't worry, I've thought it through

57
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,200
I'll marry in your place

58
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,440
Being a concubine isn't so bad anyway

59
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,360
We look the same

60
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,960
No one will find out

61
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,840
Mother, Sister said the Wang family has a ghost

62
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,640
Sister is going to be killed by the ghost

63
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,120
Let's hurry and save her

64
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,680
Your sister is doing just fine in the Wang family

65
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,800
Don't talk nonsense

66
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:46,920
Mother

67
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,600
Sister, don't worry

68
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,360
I will definitely avenge you

69
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,480
Before Second Uncle died last night

70
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,320
he kept begging Shuang'er for mercy

71
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,720
This Shuang'er is the very one my master and I

72
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,800
handled in a Bone-collecting rite three years ago

73
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,160
She really was missing her right arm

74
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:14,400
Could this case be tied to Shuang'er's death?

75
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:17,760
No, I must go to the Wang family and find out

76
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,280
I'm not going

77
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,680
I wasn't asking you to go in

78
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,440
You can't even leak a word

79
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:27,880
Get over here

80
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,400
I'm not coming over

81
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,280
I found out

82
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,600
After your Bone-collecting back then

83
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,200
Wang Sanming was possessed by a ghost

84
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:37,360
He killed the Wang Madam and many servants

85
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,720
In the end, he even burned himself alive

86
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,440
Be careful when you go to the Wang family again

87
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,000
Watch out, or that ghost may possess you too

88
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,440
You damn fatso

89
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,000
Can't you hope for something good for me?

90
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,720
Play by yourself. I'm not joining you

91
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,840
Three years

92
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:13,760
Master Cao's Bone-Collecting Shop has reopened

93
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:17,720
Now Nanwan Town has someone who can do Bone-collecting

94
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,760
This was found in the second-floor corridor

95
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,960
Paper charm

96
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:32,320
Did any wedding guest have a funeral at home today?

97
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,800
No, not that I know of

98
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:37,640
But I heard Master Cao's apprentice returned to Nanwan Town

99
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:41,560
I heard he and the Fifth Concubine had a past

100
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,920
Could they be...

101
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:48,120
Whether there's a problem, one test will tell
